summary: Baby Trump - Born with a golden rattle and a patriotic heart, Baby Trump was destined for greatness from the start. While other kids played, he mastered the blockchain, preparing to lead America into a new era of innovation and prosperity. Now, ready to take the stage, Baby Trump is on a mission to make the United States the crypto capital of the world. Together, under his guidance, we will Make America Great Again, one block at a time.
